            // same per-position pending cap TryAdmit enforces on a fresh arrival — otherwise a
            // queued toast retargeted into an already-full destination backlog grows that group's
            // pending count past MaxToasts, and ReconcileGroup would have to churn through every
            // stale queued entry there instead of dropping the oldest never-shown one. Excludes
